00:05:33.730 --> 00:05:35.550
there's one other thing
you need to be considering,

00:05:35.550 --> 00:05:38.980
and that is getting
outside of this building

00:05:38.980 --> 00:05:40.370
to the pavilion right outside here

00:05:40.370 --> 00:05:42.360
and several places along the walk way

00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:45.060
to pick up the featured books tonight.

00:05:45.060 --> 00:05:49.050
One is God Is Not Great
by Christopher Hitchens,

00:05:49.050 --> 00:05:52.280
and another one is Reasonable
Faith by William Lane Craig.

00:05:52.280 --> 00:05:55.900
These are the featured books.
[audience cheering]

00:05:55.900 --> 00:05:58.150
Pick them up, and you can
actually have them signed.

00:05:58.150 --> 00:05:59.980
To have them signed, just
walk out these building,

00:05:59.980 --> 00:06:01.870
look for all the lights,
and there's some tables

00:06:01.870 --> 00:06:04.180
out there and our distinguished
debaters will be out

00:06:04.180 --> 00:06:06.960
there signing books and
answering your toughest questions

00:06:06.960 --> 00:06:09.210
right there at the table, I'm sure.

