If you've got a lot of books at home,

00:06:11.390 --> 00:06:14.740
and in fact you own a book so
you don't need another one,

00:06:14.740 --> 00:06:17.920
perhaps you can buy
some DVDs or CDs of some

00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:20.530
dynamite debates and
lectures that Bill Craig

00:06:20.530 --> 00:06:21.780
has done around the world.

00:06:21.780 --> 00:06:23.760
These are first rate materials and our

00:06:23.760 --> 00:06:26.030
Apologetics program is
actually the center point

00:06:26.030 --> 00:06:27.540
for getting all of these,
so if you wanna get

00:06:27.540 --> 00:06:30.237
them tonight, they've got
wonderful, special deals.

00:06:30.237 --> 00:06:33.170
Check out the red flyer in your brochure

00:06:33.170 --> 00:06:34.800
and that will tell you the scoop.

