00:08:26.090 --> 00:08:28.240
so I think he will do just fine,

00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:30.820
but we're grateful for
him to come to sort of

00:08:32.670 --> 00:08:35.640
the pit of opposition at Biola University.

00:08:35.640 --> 00:08:38.050
