Great program, in fact, I
think it's one of the most

00:09:41.480 --> 00:09:43.970
important, smartest, fast
paced news and issues

00:09:43.970 --> 00:09:46.500
program on the airwaves today.

00:09:46.500 --> 00:09:47.550
So, check that out.

