Professor Hewitt is a
graduate of Harvard College

00:09:57.540 --> 00:09:59.320
and the University of Michigan Law School.

00:09:59.320 --> 00:10:01.330
He has been teaching constitutional law at

00:10:01.330 --> 00:10:04.683
Chapman University Law School
since it opened in 1995.

00:10:04.683 --> 00:10:07.080
Hugh is a frequent guest on all the big

00:10:07.080 --> 00:10:09.760
