Professor Hewitt served
for nearly six years

00:10:21.330 --> 00:10:24.090
in the Reagan Administration
in a variety of posts,

00:10:24.090 --> 00:10:27.010
including assistant
council in the White House

00:10:27.010 --> 00:10:29.920
and special assistant
to attorney's general.

00:10:29.920 --> 00:10:33.860
Don't miss his daily
blog at HughHewitt.com.

00:10:33.860 --> 00:10:36.700
He's always been so very
generous with his time

00:10:36.700 --> 00:10:39.150
toward events like these at Biola,

00:10:39.150 --> 00:10:41.360
and we are deeply grateful
for his help here tonight.

