01:42:39.500 --> 01:42:41.363
It is, and you may as well
admit it, and stick to it

01:42:41.363 --> 01:42:43.420
because it's what you're good at,

01:42:43.420 --> 01:42:44.730
it involves an act of faith.

01:42:44.730 --> 01:42:47.190
Second, on the matter
of my moral question.

