it with you, was I was told
well you couldn't do this:

01:43:07.970 --> 01:43:10.617
You couldn't say, "Father, forgive them

01:43:10.617 --> 01:43:12.550
"for they know not what they do."

01:43:12.550 --> 01:43:16.130
No, but nor could you as people
of faith, you wouldn't dare.

01:43:16.130 --> 01:43:17.730
It would be blasphemy to do it.

01:43:17.730 --> 01:43:19.920
There's only one person
who can do that even

01:43:19.920 --> 01:43:21.960
on your account so, with respect,

01:43:21.960 --> 01:43:25.090
ladies and gentlemen, I think
