excuse me that the belief will,

01:43:39.370 --> 01:43:42.410
I'll say it again, that unbelief

01:43:42.410 --> 01:43:44.403
will ensure you against wickedness.

01:43:45.250 --> 01:43:48.430
You mentioned things like
apartheid and Nazism.

01:43:48.430 --> 01:43:50.700
Well, let me just run it by you.

01:43:50.700 --> 01:43:52.667
Partly this often comes
up because people say,

01:43:52.667 --> 01:43:56.000
"What about the crimes and
wickedness of the secular world?"

